{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My grandfather, my father's father, got up every morning early in the morning and walked around in the garden in the snow so that he could greet his son when, in fact, he came home.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one morning, he overslept.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was that morning when my father actually came home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He took a taxi or whatever he did from the station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he knocked at the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother was there to open it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, uh, he was home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My grandfather was very upset that he had missed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But, uh, what happened after that was fairly traumatic, certainly for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my younger brother, Walter, perhaps didn't quite appreciate the, the, the, the situation in so far that for three weeks, we were not allowed to even say hello to our father.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was in his bedroom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the house had to be very, very quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was not well, we were being told by my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And however much we pressed and wanted to see him, th-- th-- that was not permitted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in retrospect, perhaps rightly so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He must have looked so haggard, so terrible that it may well have been a very severe shock to both of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was then 12.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My younger brother was eight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It wasn't, perhaps, the sort of scene for young boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And after about a week or so after his return, my mother asked me one morning to dig a hole in the garden.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was a terrible shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I asked her what was that for, fearing the worst, she said, just please dig it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I'll explain that later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so I dug.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember, it was a tough task because the ground was frozen.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
